title: Worst dressed at the Emmys: Kendall Jenner, Gwyneth Paltrow, Karamo Brown top the list
text:
It's the biggest night in television, but everyone's fashion didn't shine at the 71st annual Primetime Emmy Awards.

Hollywood's elite descended upon the red (purple) carpet at Los Angeles' Microsoft Theater Sunday, and, some of the stars' ensembles belonged on the style D-List.

From Billy Porter's oversized, bedazzled hat to Dascha Polanco's huge ruffled sleeves and Lena Headey's yawn-inducing pattern, these celebrities missed the mark with fashion faux pas.

In no particular order, here's a gallery of the worst-dressed stars of the night, including Kendall Jenner, Gwyneth Paltrow, Taraji P. Henson, Jenny McCarthy and "Queer Eye" star Karamo Brown.

description: It may be the biggest night in television, but everyone's fashion didn't shine at the Emmys Sunday. Here are the stars who missed the mark.
